sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import CommonHeader from "./CommonHeader"; import Title from "./Title"; import Footer from "./Footer"; import classes from "./ContactUs.module.css" const ContactUs=()=>{ return <form className={classes.form}> <div> <div> <label htmlFor="name">Name</label> <input type="text" id="name"/><br/></div> <div> <label htmlFor="email">Email Id</label> <input type="email" id="email"/><br/></div> <div> <label htmlFor="phno">Phone Number</label> <input type="number" id="phno"/><br/></div> <button type="submit">Submit</button> </div> </form> <Footer/> </React.Fragment> } export default ContactUs;
